{"tid":2346940,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英國下議院以521票對73票的壓倒式票數 通過脫歐貿易協議","createTime":"2020-12-30T15:27:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T04:51:00.000Z","uid":28114,"like":181,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"1730904425a259482778882dc30615a4c664996a","tid":2346940,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:27:33.000Z","msg":"《英國踏入新歷程碑》「通過脫歐貿易協議與全民接種疫苗」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/101138131381222/posts/267008438127523/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F101138131381222%2Fposts%2F267008438127523%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSAxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=afb9f1ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/101138131381222/posts/267008438127523/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n這夜英國有兩大喜訊，讓我們可帶著期望踏入新的一年！<br />\n<br />\n經過艱苦的一年，在踏入2021年前，英國正式進入歷史的新一頁。英國下議院以521票對73票的壓倒式票數，通過首相Boris Johnson在平安夜與歐盟達成的脫歐貿易協議。<br />\n<br />\n英國首相表示，英國將可重掌「國家命運」<br />\n&rdquo;National Destiny&rdquo;，並寄語英國國民「我們無所畏懼，即使我們間或選擇以不同方式行事！」&rdquo;....We have nothing to fear,  if sometimes we choose to do things differently.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n另一個令人心振奮的消息是，由英國研發的牛津疫苗正式獲英國監管批准。首劑牛津疫苗預計由下周一開始，可替國民接種。英國已經預訂一億劑，足以讓5000萬名國民接種（每人要兩劑）。簡單來說，那就是全民接種！現階段在兩種疫苗獲批下，年老或有健康狀況的人士會獲優先接種，預計首階段獲接種的約2500萬人，預期在一星期內可讓2百萬名人士接種。<br />\n<br />\n英國首相Boris Johnson形容，這為英國科學的一次勝利！&rdquo;A Triumph&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n傳送門：<br />\nBBC: 牛津疫苗<br />\nCovid-19: Oxford-AstraZeneca vaccine approved for use in UK <a href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/health-55280671\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fhealth-55280671&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSAxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=0668d8b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/health-55280671</a><br />\n<br />\nSky News: 英國下議院通告脫歐貿易協譵<br />\nBrexit: MPs overwhelmingly back EU-UK trade deal ahead of end of transition period <a href=\"http://news.sky.com/story/brexit-mps-overwhelmingly-back-eu-uk-trade-deal-ahead-of-end-of-transition-period-12175646\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbrexit-mps-overwhelmingly-back-eu-uk-trade-deal-ahead-of-end-of-transition-period-12175646&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSAxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=ca7d8b93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.sky.com/story/brexit-mps-overwhelmingly-back-eu-uk-trade-deal-ahead-of-end-of-transition-period-12175646</a><br />\n<br />\n#否極泰來<br />\n<br />\n圖片：BBC"},{"pid":"8bc9fe3e855ee7233268a570d288e87bc5d55671","tid":2346940,"uid":204743,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:28:28.000Z","msg":"God save the queen"},{"pid":"718e9de5b475116b72123db3a26ed4a4938068a8","tid":2346940,"uid":223741,"like":32,"dislike":3,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:28:58.000Z","msg":"呢樣野都搞咗好耐<br />\n之前投票都收咗皮幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a3eec6e26bb87369737dbbcb8de3785bf43fb5e","tid":2346940,"uid":15010,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:29:28.000Z","msg":"個deal大約內容係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b24aff6be4ce0514817de23ed121d7b984c40a29","tid":2346940,"uid":387466,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:31:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/041nXAAn714\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F041nXAAn714&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSAxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=72e3334e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/041nXAAn714</a>"},{"pid":"a60c00088651075e4d7ad274308ff37eefd03ba7","tid":2346940,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3a3eec6e26bb87369737dbbcb8de3785bf43fb5e","tid":2346940,"uid":15010,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:29:28.000Z","msg":"個deal大約內容係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:32:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http